Exercise 2
For this exercise i chose scenario A

My prompting strategy would be first to give the ai the context. In this case the context is that i need to plan an event for 20 people with 500 dollars. Next, 
i would tell the ai my role which is to be the project manager in this case as i am planning the event. After this, i would give a step-by-step plan of how i want
to plan this event. Then, i would give the requirements of what i need at this event like food, drinks, and a venue. Finally i would give the ai the time constraints 
i have to complete this planning and the budget breakdown of how i would like to spend the 500 dollars.
The reasoning behind this is that if you give every detail it will allow ai to perform the best and assist you in best way possible.
